{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">GHOST CAM is an immersive VR and PC game where you explore an abandoned bedroom which unfolds into a labyrinth armed with a camera, torch and your wits. Look for ghosts to capture in a photo, unearth the story, discover what kind of ghost expert you are \u2013 <strong>but beware...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/extras/GC_july_24_rbb2.gif?t=1733905971\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Navigate an eerie twisting set of rooms</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Walk around a haunted bedroom and beyond but be careful! If a ghost catches you the dreamscape can twist into a nightmare the deeper you go - so you may have to play more than once to unlock the full experience. If the spirits let you....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/extras/ghostcam_game_testskills.gif?t=1733905971\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Discover clues with your camera</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wield your trusty camera to find ghost traces and try to capture ghosts in a polaroid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/extras/GC_july_24_gt224.gif?t=1733905971\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Solve puzzles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Piece together ghostly traces left behind, memories and more to go further.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/extras/GC-boxes.gif?t=1733905971\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Get different results</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't accept your first ghost catching result! The more you play, the more choices you can make and the better your result.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/extras/ghostcam_game_resulth.gif?t=1733905971\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Uncover the mystery</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find out what <i>really</i> is going on beneath the domestic surface - in this world or the next...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/extras/GHOSTCAM_tutorial.gif?t=1733905971\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733905971","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733905971","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733905971","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733905971","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Supported","id":53}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">GHOST CAM is an immersive VR and PC game where you explore an abandoned bedroom which unfolds into a labyrinth armed with a camera, torch and your wits. Look for ghosts to capture in a photo, unearth the story, discover what kind of ghost expert you are \u2013 <strong>but beware...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121930/extras/GC_july_24_rbb2